-- Assuming Stone Duality, we can derive MP:
-- From Stone Duality: evaluation map B ‚Üí 2^(Sp B) is an equivalence for B : BooleŌČ
-- Given őĪ : 2^‚Ąē with ¬¨(‚ąÄn. őĪn = 0), consider the quotient 2/őĪ.
-- If Sp(2/őĪ) were inhabited, we'd have a map 2/őĪ ‚Üí 2,
